headline: 2 Internet Stocks to Keep an Eye On and 1 We Question
summary: Whether it be online shopping or social media, secular forces are propelling consumer internet businesses forward. These themes have enabled rapid growth for the industry, which has posted a 36.9% gain over the past six months compared to 26% for the S&P 500.

headline: Dialogue AI Closes $6M Seed Round to Bring Live, AI-led Customer Research to Every Team
summary: LOS ANGELES, October 17, 2025--Dialogue AI, an AI-native market research platform powered by a live conversational AI interviewer and built to serve teams across the business, launched today with a $6M seed round. The round was led by Lightspeed Venture Partners, with participation from Seven Stars, Uncommon Projects, the Tornante Company (founded by Michael Eisner), and notable angels, including the CPO of Discord, former CPO of Nextdoor, and former CTO of Match Group.

headline: Assessing Match Group (MTCH) Valuation Following Recent Share Price Decline
summary: Match Group (MTCH) shares have seen some pressure over the past month, with the stock declining about 14%. Investors are weighing the current environment in comparison to the company's recent growth in both revenue and net income. See our latest analysis for Match Group.
